@startuml sequence
title Fluxo de Detecção com Fusão: POST /detection/fused

actor Client as C
participant "FastAPI\nAPI Server" as API
participant "Image Utils\nUtils" as IMG
participant "HTTP Client\nAsyncClient" as HTTP
participant "vLLM Server\nQwen" as QWEN_SRV
participant "YOLOE Service\nServices" as YOLOE
participant "Fusion Service\nServices" as FUSION
participant "Response\nSerialization" as SER

C ->> API: POST /detection/fused
activate API

API ->> IMG: resize_base64_image(image)
activate IMG
note over IMG: Redimensiona se\nnecessário (max 1024px)
IMG -->> API: image_b64_resized
deactivate IMG

API ->> IMG: b64_to_pil(image_b64)
activate IMG
note over IMG: Converte para\nPIL Image
IMG -->> API: img (PIL)
deactivate IMG

API ->> API: Inicia chamadas paralelas
par Execução Paralela
    API ->> HTTP: POST /v1/chat/completions (Qwen + image)
    HTTP ->> QWEN_SRV: Processa imagem
    QWEN_SRV -->> HTTP: choices: content JSON
    HTTP -->> API: vllm_response
else
    API ->> YOLOE: run_yoloe(img)
    YOLOE -->> API: yoloe_objects: List of DetectedObject
end
note over API: Qwen processa imagem\nYOLOE executa detecção\nAmbos executam em paralelo

API ->> API: parse_qwen_response(vllm_response)
note over API: Extrai JSON e valida\nobservações do Qwen
API ->> API: qwen_objects: List of DetectedObject

API ->> FUSION: fuse_by_iou(qwen_objects, yoloe_objects)
activate FUSION
note over FUSION: IoU threshold = 0.15\nPara cada Qwen object:\nbusca melhor match YOLOE

loop Para cada qwen_object
    FUSION ->> FUSION: calcula IoU com cada yoloe_bbox
    alt IoU >= 0.15 e nao usado
        FUSION ->> FUSION: cria objeto fusionado\nlabel+score Qwen + bbox YOLOE
    else IoU < 0.15
        FUSION ->> FUSION: mantem objeto Qwen
    end
end

FUSION -->> API: fused_objects: List of DetectedObject
deactivate FUSION

API ->> SER: serialize_detections(fused_objects)
activate SER
note over SER: Formata para JSON\nresponse da API
SER -->> API: objects e too_many_objects: false
deactivate SER

API -->> C: HTTP 200
deactivate API

note over C, SER
  Total: Qwen + YOLOE em paralelo
  Fusao por IoU combina resultado
  Resposta: objetos com melhor confianca
end note

@enduml